    "capped_discovery": {
      "description": "A topic storm under one wildcard monitor. Discovery stops at the per-monitor cap (max_topics here overrides MAX_TOPICS_PER_MONITOR to 2 for a compact fixture) and the capped flag is raised; already-tracked topics keep updating, the overflow topic is dropped.",
